            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-slate-800 mb-4">Timeline of Mainstream Popularity</h2>
             <p class="text-center text-slate-600 mb-4 text-sm max-w-3xl mx-auto">This chart illustrates the rise and fall of mainstream popularity for each major genre wave. Hover over the chart to see which sounds were dominating the rock landscape at any given point from the early '90s through the 2000s. It provides a visual overview of the transitions discussed in this exploration.</p>
